CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 8, 1965, pg. 24, reads: "Champions - Members of the Central Baptist Church cage team, champions of the Centre Avenue YMCA Church League, were honored at a league banquet, at Central Baptist Church, recently. Shown are, left to right, front row: Joseph Franklin, coach; Ronald Wright, Dean Oliver, Ray Hath, Robert Johnson, George Meyers, and Charles Scray.  in back row are Michael Simms, Wilburn Thompson, Gary White, Kenneth King, captain of the team; James Whitman and Biddie Adams. - Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of eight young men from Central Baptist Church basketball team, posed behind table with trophies
